public static void forwardDCT8(float[] vector)
Fast forward Dct using AA&N. Taken from the book "JPEG still image data compression standard", by Pennebaker and Mitchell, chapter 4, figure "4-8".

inverseDCT8

public static void inverseDCT8(float[] vector)
Fast inverse Dct using AA&N. This is taken from the beautiful http://vsr.informatik.tu-chemnitz.de/~jan/MPEG/HTML/IDCT.html which gives easy equations and properly explains constants and scaling factors. Terms have been inlined and the negation optimized out of existence.
